help-plugins:
Ikhenela izibambo kuphela ukuphathwa lomsebenzisi, ama-plugin kanye namakhasi. Ukuze konke okunye une-plugin. ukulandaune itholakale-plugin main. Khetha yibo okudingayo. Kukhona konke futhi uhlu olusha njalo.
-plugin ozifakile -plugin. Ungakwazi ukwengeza ama-plugin ngesandla, uma uthanda, futhi ungakwazi ukuvula noma ukuvala ngisho uzisuse.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, zonke ezimali lokukhokhisa kanye eziyisisekelo iyiswe plugin facturacion_base. Ungalanda ngokuzenzakalelayo futhi uyifake ngokuchofoza le nkinobho.

cron-still-working: IPHUTHA: Kukhona kakade cron ukugijima. Uma ucabanga ukuthi kulungile, iya Admin > uhlelo Imininingwane ukuxazulula le nkinga.
data-out-of-range: Usuku akhethiwe lingaphandle wonyaka. It is akhethiwe kangcono.
resumed-company-name-less-than-company-n: Igama iDemo %1$s kumelwe abe mfushane kuka igama.
help-help: Enemininingwane imibuzo noma izinkinga zakho uma ufuna ukuba iphendulwe.
a-lot-of-plugins: ama-plugin engaphezu kwengu-50 nge ukuthuthukiswa ekhuthele kakhulu.
help-demo-facturascripts: Lokhu demo esetshenziswa ukuthola umqondo okusheshayo kanjani FacturaScripts isebenza ngenombolo encishisiwe plugin asebenzayo futhi ongakhetha zabaningi abakhubazekile. Qaphela ukuthi kukhona inqwaba yabantu usebenzisa le demo ngesikhathi.

required-php-version: FacturaScripts kudingeka PHP 5.3 noma ngaphezulu, futhi une PHP %1$s.

cant-write-tmp-folder: Awukwazi ukubhala mayelana FacturaScripts ifolda tmp

are-you-new-developer: Ingabe uMklami futhi ozama ukwenza plugin?

cant-write-facturascripts-folder: ifolda FacturaScripts akanawo izimvume zokubhala. Lezi izimvume kudingeka uhlelo isifanekiso, ukufaka ama-plugin, izibuyekezo, njll...
error-connecting-database: Awukwazi ukuxhuma database. Hlola idatha yomsebenzisi nephasiwedi.
help-database-socket: Kuphela kwezinye hostings kumelwe ucacise MySQL isokhethi.
help-distributions: Ukulungiselelwa okuzenzakalelayo yalezi kukaMoya, okungukuthi SELinux, amabhlogo noma imiphi imizamo ukuqinisekisa ukuthi ngabe folda izimvume zokubhala. Ikhubaza noma lishintsha ukucushwa SELinux for ekusebenzeni kahle FacturaScripts.
help-hosting: Uzama ukubhala izimvume ezivela FTP noma cPanel.
help-linux: Lo myalo ukuzixazulula inkinga-95 % amacala, kodwa ungakwazi ukuphuma for isixazululo abazwela ngokweqile, wena umane kudingeka Apache (noma PHP) ukufunda nokubhala kufolda.
help-memcached: Lesi sigaba ngokuphelele ozikhethela. Uma ozifakile memcached, ungacacisa lapha umzila, amatheku Isiqalo ukuyisebenzisa. Kungenjalo, shiya ke njengoba.
help-openssl: FacturaScripts idinga isandiso OpenSSL ukulanda plugin, izibuyekezo bese uthumela ama-imeyili.
help-openssl-linux: Akuvamile kakhulu a PHP self ukufaka ku-Linux akubandakanyi OpenSSL. Zama ukufaka iphakethe php-opensslnomphathi wakho iphakethe bese uqale kabusha Apache. Ukuze uthole olunye ulwazi bheka Usizo izinkundla noma i-Linux ukusatshalaliswa oyisebenzisayo.
help-openssl-mac: Akuvamile ukuthi i-Apache + PHP + MySQL ye-Mac emaphaketheni akubandakanyi OpenSSL. Sinikeza ahlukahlukene zahlanganiswa ne konke okudingayo yethu kwesigaba href = "https://www.facturascripts.com/descargar?mac=TRUE" Ukulanda.
help-us:
Khumbula ukuthi unayo Usizo Imenyuphezulu kwesokudla. Uma uthola izinkinga, chofoza Iphutha Umbiko...futhi uchaza yakho umbuzo, isiphakamiso noma amaphutha uthola. Senza isofthiwe abaphelele, kodwa ngosizo lwakho singakwazi fikisa us closer
;-) Futhi khumbula une section ekhethekile elalinikezelwe Ukufakwaamaphepha ethu esemthethweni:
help-use-this-form-for-help: Sebenzisa leli fomu ukuze usazise. Imininingwane engeziwe linanyathelisiwe FacturaScripts version oyisebenzisayo, uhlu lwama-plugin asebenzayo, PHP inguqulo, njll...
help-ziparchive: FacturaScripts ZipArchive idinga isandiso ukuba decompress-plugin izibuyekezo.
installed-obsolete-php: FacturaScripts kudingeka PHP 5.3 noma ngaphezulu. Usebenzisa inguqulo %1$s.
official-package-for-windows: FacturaScripts ukunikela inguqulo ye-Windows zonkeisofthiwe ezidingekayo (ezifana OpenSSL) esivele ifakiwe njengoba standard. Ungakwazi encontrala esigabeni = "https://www.facturascripts.com/descargar?windows=TRUE" Ukulanda.
point-isnt-the-default-decimal-separator: I isihlukanisi idesimali ekule nguqulo PHP akulona iphuzu, njengoba ezisezikhungweni ejwayelekile. Kufanele ukulilungisa.
required-mbstring: FacturaScripts mbstring isandiso kudingeka sisebenze nezinhlamvu okungezona European (Chinese, isiKorea, Japanese futhi Russian).
simplexml-not-found: Awukwazi ukuthola isandiso simplexml e ukufakwa kwakho PHP. Kuzomele ufake noma kusebenze.
unofficial-package-for-windows: Uma unquma ukusebenzisa a emaphaketheni ehlukene, bese lokhu akubandakanyi kudingekile, kufanele ufune usizo ezithangamini noma ukusekela abadali isembozo.
answer-2-installed-on-hosting: Udlule quota we ibamba. hostings abaningi babe imikhawulo ukusetshenziswa database, futhi uma overdo ukuvimba.
answer-2-installed-on-pc: Uguqule iphasiwedi database. Ukuze ulungise lokhu kumelwe nakanjani uyibuyisele nephasiwedi yokuqala kusukela database noma ukubeka iphasiwedi entsha ku FacturaScripts ifayela config.php.
answer-3-installed-on-hosting: Lokho kwashintsha iphasiwedi noma ukumisa egciniwe.
help-cant-connect-database: Akwenzekanga ukuba ukuxhuma database. Izizathu ngokuvamile ezahlukene kuye ngokuthi lapho une FacturaScripts ezifakiwe.
config-not-found: ifayela config.php ayitholakalanga. Awukwazi uthuthukise ngaphandle kokufaka.
dont-know-your-keys: Awazi iphasiwedi yini yakho? Ungakwazi uthintane ngokuchofoza Buka inkinobho ke okhiye bami.
help-adminlte: Sisebenze ku isakhiwo esishaukunikeza FacturaScripts zanamuhla bheka nohlangothi imenyu entsha, okuhlangene search engine, umsebenzisi ibonakale kakhudlwana, imifanekiso ngaphezulu futhi kangcono nokunye. Lona ngumphumela.
